        "action": "Reduce the maximum working hours to 30 hours per week after Covid-19 lockdown",
        "additional_details": "This could help maintain the enhanced quality of life enjoyed by many during the lockdown: family time, health: time to walk, run or cycle, time to garden or be in nature, reduced work-related stress and increased happiness.",
        "background": "The Government should reduce the maximum number of working hours to 30 per week, with a view to better sharing out the work available and enhancing quality of life.",
